MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Pipeline: Ingest → AI Classify → Qualify → Score → Deep Enrich → GHL Push

Core modules:
- lead_engine/score_and_push.py: 6-step pipeline orchestrator
- lead_engine/qualify.py: $2M-$100M filter, 4 deal tiers (SMALL/CORE/LARGE/INSTITUTIONAL)
- lead_engine/scoring.py: 5-dimension composite scoring (0-100, T1-T4)

Enrichment (5 layers, ~$0.32/lead):
- enrichment/entity_resolution: CT/MA/RI/FL/TX SOS + OpenCorporates + Grok AI
- enrichment/skip_trace: BatchSkip + PropStream + REISkip + free lookup + DNC
- enrichment/property_data: ATTOM API (owner, mortgage, equity, market value)
- enrichment/news_intel: Google News + court records + zoning/litigation flags
- enrichment/contractor_intel: Cross-permit GC reverse lookup

GHL Integration:
- ghl_integration/client.py: Contact upsert with skip trace phone/email
- 60+ custom fields: scoring, entity, skip trace, property, news, contractor
- Tags: tier, source, has-contact-info, dnc-verified

Permit Ingestion:
- openshovels/schema.py: StandardPermit + EnrichmentBundle Pydantic models
- openshovels/jurisdictions/ct_hartford: ArcGIS Hub scraper (34K records)
- openshovels/pipeline/enrich.py: Grok AI bulk classification
