-# REAL-ESTATE-LEAD-GEN
-REAL ESTATE LEAD GEN
+# TILT Construction Lead Engine
+
+**Permit Data → AI Scoring → Deep Enrichment → Contact Discovery → GoHighLevel CRM**
+
+Automated construction lending lead generation engine that ingests building permits from public open data portals, scores them against TILT lending criteria, enriches qualified leads with entity resolution and skip tracing, and pushes actionable contacts into GoHighLevel for sales outreach.
+
+## Architecture
+
+```
+┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
+│                    TILT LEAD ENGINE PIPELINE                     │
+├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
+│                                                                 │
+│  1. INGEST          Scrape permits from jurisdiction portals    │
+│       ↓             (ArcGIS, Socrata, CSV open data)            │
+│  2. AI CLASSIFY     Grok AI: project type, NOO, value est.     │
+│       ↓             ($0.002/permit)                              │
+│  3. QUALIFY         Filter: $2M-$100M, 4 deal tiers             │
+│       ↓             SMALL / CORE / LARGE / INSTITUTIONAL        │
+│  4. SCORE           5-dimension composite scoring (0-100)       │
+│       ↓             T1 HOT → T2 WARM → T3 NURTURE → T4 MONITOR │
+│  5. DEEP ENRICH     Entity, Skip Trace, Property, News, GC     │
+│       ↓             (~$0.32/lead for T1-T3)                     │
+│  6. GHL PUSH        Contact + Opportunity + 60+ custom fields  │
+│                                                                 │
+└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
+```
+
+## Usage
+
+```bash
+# Full pipeline with enrichment
+python lead_engine/score_and_push.py -j ct_hartford --since 2024-01-01
+
+# Dry run (score + enrich but skip GHL push)
+python lead_engine/score_and_push.py -j ct_hartford --dry-run
+
+# Skip deep enrichment (scoring only)
+python lead_engine/score_and_push.py -j ct_hartford --skip-enrichment
+
+# Only entity resolution + skip trace
+python lead_engine/score_and_push.py -j ct_hartford --enrich-layers entity,skip_trace
+
+# Limit permits processed
+python lead_engine/score_and_push.py -j ct_hartford --limit 100
+
+# Scheduled mode (every 15 minutes)
+python lead_engine/score_and_push.py --scheduled
+```
+
+## Setup
+
+```bash
+pip install -r requirements.txt
+cp config/.env.example config/.env
+# Edit config/.env with API keys
+```
+
+## Calculus Holdings LLC — Confidential
